256
00:20:57.703 --> 00:21:01.540
- Ya lo está, Squints.
- Cállate.


257
00:21:01.582 --> 00:21:04.042
Ya te lo dije, Benny.

258
00:21:06.003 --> 00:21:08.839
Smalls, lánzala a la segunda.

259
00:21:09.256 --> 00:21:10.465
Vale.

260
00:21:12.634 --> 00:21:14.720
Otra vez no.

261
00:21:14.761 --> 00:21:17.097
